{"tid":810973,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"1百萬美元總獎金：NASA公開火星化學比賽","createTime":"2018-09-08T12:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T08:35:06.000Z","uid":165773,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1b59a2c5966ac1c85435b5a3878cb8e5c3141b59","tid":810973,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"NASA Offers $1M for Producing Sugar on Mars <a href=\"https://www.pcmag.com/news/363601/nasa-offers-1m-for-producing-sugar-on-mars\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmag.com%2Fnews%2F363601%2Fnasa-offers-1m-for-producing-sugar-on-mars&d=Fc73ds4qqqpJJjdPsHF6JbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=610fe3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmag.com/news/363601/nasa-offers-1m-for-producing-sugar-on-mars</a><br />\n<br />\n報名登記截止：今年一月廿四日<br />\n二月廿三交proposal deadline<br />\n入圍第一round 會有五個idea<br />\n每個idea有5萬美元獎金<br />\n入左圍就要做實驗示範個idea<br />\n贏左會贏埋餘下75萬美元獎金<br />\n<br />\n大目標：幫人在火星上生存<br />\n小目標：減少火星大氣既CO2<br />\n比賽題目：如何將火星CO2變glucose<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.co2conversionchallenge.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.co2conversionchallenge.org%2F&d=Fc73ds4qqqpJJjdPsHF6JbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6dd626fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.co2conversionchallenge.org/</a>"},{"pid":"7caec9cbf1662d5832dac44e60ad3214b58b66ff","tid":810973,"uid":14299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:10:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"25e0d9381d7474dbf4af23cc69109ad59f13046d","tid":810973,"uid":4526,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"137e36b7eb71c167f0e112c78ffa9e3954a5fb5d","tid":810973,"uid":3775,"like":2,"dislike":50,"score":-48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"其實好難諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無理由咁白痴走去講 photosynthesis 既pathways <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/